+## Run Doctor
+
+```bash
+flowai-workflow runs doctor --workflow .flowai-workflow/github-inbox --run <run-id>
+flowai-workflow runs doctor --workflow .flowai-workflow/github-inbox --run <run-id> --repair
+flowai-workflow runs doctor --workflow .flowai-workflow/github-inbox --run <run-id> --json
+```
+
+`runs doctor` checks one run's `journal.jsonl`, replay invariants,
+declared node directories, orphan node directories, and stale lock. Repair is
+limited to removing a torn final journal line and deleting a stale lock for
+the selected run.
+
